<div class="whl-page">

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <div class="whl-hero">
    <div class="wave-field" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="wave wave--back"></span>
      <span class="wave wave--mid"></span>
      <span class="wave wave--front"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="whl-hero-inner">
      <div class="whl-eyebrow">Wholesale · Now Onboarding Retailers</div>
      <h1 class="whl-title">Put Happie on your shelf.</h1>
      <p class="whl-sub">Caffeine-free, all-natural sparkling drinks made with functional mushrooms — the non-alcoholic option shoppers are actually looking for. Retail-ready 6-packs and master cases, third-party tested every batch.</p>
      <a href="#order" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Start a Wholesale Order →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── WHY STOCK US ── -->
  <div class="whl-section">
    <div class="whl-inner">
      <div class="whl-section-head">
        <div class="whl-section-eyebrow">Why Retailers Stock Happie</div>
        <h2 class="whl-section-title">A can that earns its shelf space</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="whl-grid">
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3h18v4H3zM5 7v13h14V7M9 11h6"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Retail-ready</h3>
          <p>Shelf-stable, retail-priced 6-packs and 24-can master cases. Loose and case formats available for however your set is built.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M8 12l3 3 5-6"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>The category shoppers want</h3>
          <p>Non-alcoholic, caffeine-free, and functional — sitting right where better-for-you soda, sparkling water and alcohol alternatives are growing fastest.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l7 4v5c0 4-3 7-7 9-4-2-7-5-7-9V7z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Tested every batch</h3>
          <p>Third-party lab tested at an ISO/IEC 17025-accredited lab. Certificates of Analysis available for every batch you carry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 7h16M6 7V5h12v2M8 7v13h8V7"/><path d="M10 11h4"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Bold on the shelf</h3>
          <p>Three high-contrast flavors — Blue Razzberry, Mango Mimosa, Watermelon — with can art built to catch an eye from across the aisle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── ORDERING CARD (links out to Airgoods) ── -->
  <div class="whl-section whl-order-section" id="order">
    <div class="whl-inner">

      {%- comment -%}
        Set airgoods_url to the Happie Fusion Airgoods store URL. We link OUT to
        Airgoods rather than embedding its widget: the embed pulls the connected
        catalog, which is not what we sell on this site. Until the URL is set,
        the button falls back to an email order so the page never ships a dead
        link. To go live, replace PASTE_AIRGOODS_URL with the real link.
      {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- comment -%} Airgoods store (airgoods.com/u/happie) currently lists the THC "Social Tonic" line alongside Fungi Fusion — button stays on the email fallback until that catalog is cleaned. {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- assign airgoods_url = 'PASTE_AIRGOODS_URL' -%}
      {%- assign ag_ready = false -%}
      {%- if airgoods_url != 'PASTE_AIRGOODS_URL' and airgoods_url != blank -%}{%- assign ag_ready = true -%}{%- endif -%}

      <div class="ag-card">
        <div class="ag-card-body">
          <div class="ag-lockup">
            <img src="{{ 'happie-logo.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Happie" class="ag-lockup-logo" width="120" height="36" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="ag-lockup-x">&times;</span>
            <span class="ag-lockup-partner">airgoods</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ag-card-title">Order wholesale from us today</h3>
          <p class="ag-card-partner">We've partnered with <strong>Airgoods</strong> — the wholesale marketplace for specialty food &amp; beverage stores — to make stocking Happie easy.</p>

          <div class="ag-perks">
            <div class="ag-perk">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg>
              <span>Buy now, pay 60 days later*</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ag-perk">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 3h15v13H1zM16 8h4l3 3v5h-7"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
              <span>Free shipping for 3 months*</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ag-perk">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="12" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2.5"/></svg>
              <span>$50 to spend on your first order*</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="ag-fine">*For buyers new to Airgoods.</p>

          {%- if ag_ready -%}
            <a href="{{ airgoods_url }}" class="btn-primary btn-lg ag-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shop Wholesale on Airgoods →</a>
          {%- else -%}
            <a href="mailto:{{ shop.email }}?subject=Wholesale%20order%20—%20Happie%20Fusion" class="btn-primary btn-lg ag-btn">Contact Us to Order →</a>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>

        <div class="ag-card-media" aria-hidden="true">
          {%- assign ag_img = all_products['happie-fungi-fusion-mushroom-drink-variety-pack'].featured_image -%}
          {%- unless ag_img -%}{%- assign ag_img = all_products['blue-razzberry-fungi-powered-seltzer'].featured_image -%}{%- endunless -%}
          {% if ag_img %}
            <img src="{{ ag_img | image_url: width: 720 }}" alt="Happie Fungi Fusion lineup" width="720" height="720" loading="lazy" />
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="whl-contact">Questions before you order? <a href="mailto:{{ shop.email }}?subject=Wholesale%20inquiry%20—%20Happie%20Fusion">{{ shop.email }}</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
.whl-hero {
  position: relative; isolation: isolate; overflow: hidden;
  text-align: center; padding: 84px 24px 96px;
  --wave-color: #2D6A4F;
  background-color: #FCF9F4;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(56% 125% at  8% 30%, rgba(45,200,214,0.42)  0%, rgba(45,200,214,0)  62%),
    radial-gradient(52% 120% at 30% 82%, rgba(82,205,150,0.40)  0%, rgba(82,205,150,0)  62%),
    radial-gradient(50% 118% at 52% 14%, rgba(255,190,60,0.36)  0%, rgba(255,190,60,0)  60%),
    radial-gradient(54% 122% at 74% 80%, rgba(255,122,138,0.34) 0%, rgba(255,122,138,0) 62%),
    radial-gradient(56% 125% at 95% 26%, rgba(138,96,232,0.38)  0%, rgba(138,96,232,0)  62%);
  background-size: 200% 200%, 215% 215%, 190% 190%, 225% 225%, 235% 235%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  animation: navSilk 26s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .whl-hero { animation: none; } }
.whl-hero > *:not(.wave-field) { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.whl-hero-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
.whl-eyebrow {
  display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); border: 1px solid rgba(45,106,79,0.16);
  padding: 7px 15px; border-radius: 50px; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.whl-title { font-size: clamp(34px,5.4vw,58px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #16181B; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.whl-sub { font-size: 17px; color: #3F4A43; line-height: 1.65; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 28px; }

.whl-section { padding: 72px 24px; }
.whl-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
.whl-inner--narrow { max-width: 820px; }
.whl-section-head { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 44px; }
.whl-section-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green, #2D6A4F); margin-bottom: 10px; }
.whl-section-title { font-size: clamp(24px,3.4vw,38px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }

.whl-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
.whl-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07); border-radius: 20px; padding: 26px 22px; box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
.whl-card-icon { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 50%; background: #EEF7F1; color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F); margin-bottom: 14px; }
.whl-card h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.whl-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.65; }

.whl-order-section { background: #F6F8F7; }

/* Airgoods CTA card */
.ag-card {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr; align-items: stretch;
  background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-radius: 26px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 54px rgba(0,0,0,0.10); overflow: hidden;
}
.ag-card-body { padding: 44px 44px 40px; }
.ag-lockup { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.ag-lockup-logo { height: 52px; width: auto; }
.ag-lockup-x { font-size: 20px; color: var(--gray, #6B6B6B); }
.ag-lockup-partner {
  font-weight: 800; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: #6C4BF0;
}
.ag-card-title { font-size: clamp(24px,2.6vw,32px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #16181B; }
.ag-card-partner { font-size: 15px; color: #555; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 24px; max-width: 460px; }
.ag-perks { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.ag-perk {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
  padding: 16px 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border-radius: 14px;
  background: #FBFCFB; color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F);
}
.ag-perk span { font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 600; color: #333; line-height: 1.4; }
.ag-fine { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray, #6B6B6B); margin-bottom: 26px; }
.ag-btn { display: inline-block; }

.ag-card-media {
  position: relative;
  background: #fff;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.ag-card-media img {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover; object-position: center;
}

.whl-contact { text-align: center; margin-top: 22px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray, #6B6B6B); }
.whl-contact a { color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .whl-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .ag-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .ag-card-media { order: -1; min-height: 240px; }
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .whl-hero { padding: 60px 18px 72px; }
  .whl-section { padding: 48px 16px; }
  .whl-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .ag-card-body { padding: 30px 24px 34px; }
  .ag-perks { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .ag-perk { flex-direction: row; align-items: center; }
